#GuruDakshina- A tribute to the ones who inspire us by Classplus

Punishment se achievement tak, teachers have always gone the extra mile to make our lives special. They are the ones who shaped our lives and inspired us to be the best version of ourselves. This teachers’ day, let us revisit the fond memories of our student life and celebrate the ones who helped us grow.
Now is our time to pay #GuruDakshina to them and support them in all their endeavours.
